{"article_id":"wPSryxsIlYFQf4PF","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"It ' s a bit difficult to fathom the sort of person","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"who would defend","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"- explicitly or implicitly -","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"the conduct of police officers in Ferguson , Missouri , over the last week .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"The people","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"tasked with protecting the community and enforcing the law","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"transformed the small city into a mini-war zone , with explosions in the streets , assault rifles","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"trained on unarmed protesters ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"rubber projectiles fired in abundance ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"and tear gas canisters fired through residential neighborhoods .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Along the way they arrested a couple of journalists for no reason ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"threatened to arrest a few others ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"and deployed tear gas against a TV news crew .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"And they did all that in response to protests over the fatal shooting","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"- by a police officer -","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"of Michael Brown , an unarmed black teenager .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Those protests escalated","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"( into riots and looting , in some cases )","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"after the police refused to release the name of the officer or any other information","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that might help explain why a young black man was killed at the hands of a police force","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"that has long faced accusations of racial discrimination .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"After the governor stepped in","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"and put the highway patrol in charge of security ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"the Ferguson police finally came forward with some information :","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"the name of the officer","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"who killed Brown ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"and a police report and video surveillance footage","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"implicating Brown as a suspect in the robbery of a convenience store .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Releasing the video only stoked further outrage ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"as it appeared that the Ferguson police were trying to disparage the character of the victim","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"( the police chief later acknowledged","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"that the robbery had nothing to do with Brown 's shooting ) .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"The Justice Department had asked the police not to release the video out of concern","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"that it would spark unrest .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"That ' s not a track record","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"anyone can be proud of","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"( save for the St. Louis County police chief ,","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"who described the above actions as the product of \" a remarkable amount of restraint \" ) .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"And yet , segments of the conservative pundit world are doing what they can","depth":3},{"id":39,"text":"to defend the Ferguson cops ,","depth":4},{"id":40,"text":"or least deflect blame for the escalation away from them .","depth":4},{"id":41,"text":"Last Wednesday night ,","depth":4},{"id":42,"text":"as Ferguson police were lobbing tear gas at peaceful protesters ,","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"Fox News ' Martha MacCallum ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"sitting in for Megyn Kelly ,","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"put together a news segment and a panel discussion on the threat","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"posed by the presence of one or two New Black Panther Party members among the protesters .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"\" Let 's start with this , this Black Panther issue , \"","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"MacCallum told her guests ,","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"\" because the FBI is very concerned about this","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"and","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"when I went on the Facebook page today of the leader of this group , Chawn Kweli ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"it was astonishing to me the things","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"that he is saying on his Facebook page . \"","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"That same evening , Sean Hannity interviewed Ferguson police chief Thomas Jackson","depth":4},{"id":55,"text":"and teed up some leading questions","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"that helped Jackson cast police actions as a response to violence from protesters .","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"On the issue","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"of concealing the identity of the officer","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"who shot Brown ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Hannity prefaced the question","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"by citing the New Black Panthers , Louis Farrakhan , death threats , Al Sharpton , threatening graffiti , and looting :","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"HANNITY :","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"I understand","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"that the police officer -","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"there ' s been a lot of death threats against him , a lot of volatility .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"You ' ve got the New Black Panther Party ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"Louis Farrakhan has spoken out ,","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"the Reverend Al Sharpton is there .","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"You ' ve had the chanting -","depth":15},{"id":70,"text":"you have a sign up there ,","depth":15},{"id":71,"text":"the only good cop is a dead cop .","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"There ' s been rioting and loot , etc .","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"going on .","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"That has prevented you from releasing the name of the officer .","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"Some have questioned the wisdom of that -","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"the public ' s right","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"to know","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"versus the safety of the officer .","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"Are you balancing that ?","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"On Friday night , glibertarian homunculus Greg Gutfeld gave the Ferguson police every justification for their actions .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"`` You ca n't stop anarchy with a stern look , ''","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"said the same guy","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"who used the word `` fascism ''","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"to describe people","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"who complained about an airline 's promotional video .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Even before the Ferguson police released any info","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"pertaining to Brown 's involvement in the convenience store theft ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"a sizable portion of the online right was doing everything","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"it could","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"to paint Brown as a dangerous gang member","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"( with the all-too-obvious suggestion","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"that his death was deserved ) .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"Reactions like these are noteworthy","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"not just for their implied tolerance of real abuses of authority ,","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"but also because there were plenty of other conservatives","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"who harshly came down on the Ferguson police .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"The general thinking is that the right is divided between the tough-on-crime conservatives","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"who will always give the police the benefit of the doubt ,","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"and the more libertarian-leaning conservatives","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"who view police abuses as violations of civil liberties and an extension of out-of-control government .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"\" If you want an indication","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"about where someone sits on the dividing line between conservative and libertarian ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"sometimes it ' s as simple as how they answer this question :","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"how do you feel about cops ? \"","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"The Federalist ' s Ben Domenech wrote Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"But the fact","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"that this divide persists","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"even in the face of such flagrant abuses as the ones","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"we saw in Ferguson","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"suggests something else is at play ,","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"and I think","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"part of it comes down to how certain conservatives define their worldview .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"People like Hannity and Fox News cretins","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"who troll around on Twitter","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"identify as conservative ,","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"but often it seems like a lot of the opinions","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"they espouse","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"are simply \" anti-liberal. \"","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"It ' s ideology by reflex :","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"If liberals support it ,","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"I don ' t ;","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"if liberals hate it ,","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"I support it .","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"And so","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"when protests erupt over a cop","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"killing an unarmed black teenager ,","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"it 's crucial","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"- absolutely crucial -","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"that photos of the victim","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"flashing `` gang signs ''","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"be plastered all over the internet .","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"When Ferguson police use military-grade weaponry against unarmed people","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"protesting what they believe was a racially motivated shooting ,","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"it 's necessary to point out that there are some very dangerous New Black Panthers in the area .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"When a couple of \" liberal media \" reporters get roughed up and handcuffed in a McDonald 's by cops","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"who \" didn ' t know better ,","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"\" some conservatives take the side of the cops","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"because the alternative","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"- siding with the liberals -","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"is anathema .","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":281,"left":181,"right":280,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":178,"right":180,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":178,"left":144,"right":177,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":143,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":143,"left":0,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":173,"right":176,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":160,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":152,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":149,"right":151,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":149,"left":145,"right":148,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":146,"right":147,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":146,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":151,"left":10,"right":150,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":159,"left":154,"right":158,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":153,"right":15,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":13,"ri